title: Print, "Detail of the Combat sculpture on the Dewey Arch, Madison Square, New York", 1899
inscribed: bottom printed in black ink: The Combat
creditline: Gift of Mrs. Arnold W. Brunner
description: Detail of the sculpture The Combat on the Dewey Arch. In the sculpture men with weapons such as a tank are gathered at the bottom. An angel holding a spear and shield floats above them.
